data.description: Have you been searching for your dream home? Look no further! This 4 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom home with resort style amenities is sure to meet all of your family???s needs! This gorgeous 2,791 square foot home (located in the much desired Cobblestone Park neighborhood) features a 2 car garage, a beautiful lawn, and fresh interior paint. Walk in to an open floor plan to unite the formal dining room, family room, and eat-in kitchen - all featuring high ceilings and beautiful hardwood floors. The eat-in kitchen features all stainless steel appliances, granite counter tops, an island, pantry, and recessed lighting. This dream kitchen poses as the perfect place to entertain guests while being large enough to support the entire family! Upstairs, you???ll find new upgraded premium carpet throughout, and ceiling fans in every room. The Master suite is the perfect place to relax after a long day - enjoy a garden tub, standing tile shower, dual vanity, and 2 large walk-in closets. You???ll find 3 additional bedrooms and spacious loft area that could be used as an office space or child???s play area! Outside, welcome to your dream backyard! Completely fenced in, swing in a hammock under the shade from the trees, grill out on the patio, or relax by the firepit with friends! Take advantage of the fantastic amenities- golf, tennis complex, pool, clubhouse, on site dining, and fitness center. This home will not last long on the market, so be sure to schedule a showing today!
